Main - Class in edu.ccsu.designpatterns.logger
This class does a simple demonstration of a file logger where messages are logged at various log levels to a file, then some observers are added to listen for when logging events happen and if relevent write the event to the console as well.
Main - Class in edu.ccsu.designpatterns.pvz
This demo of the the Observer pattern that occurs in Plants vs Zombies Heroes where one type of zombie (a Mime) observes the game and if any game piece does a bonus attack it mimics it and also carries out a bonus attack
